Package users

Class UserTest

java.lang.Object
testframework.BaseTest
users.UserTest
public class UserTest
extends BaseTest
Test class for the abstract User class. Tests base functionality shared by all user types including: - Common property getters and setters - Interface implementation - Null value handling - String representation

Uses a concrete TestUser implementation to test the abstract class.
